snippet: Defenseman Lubomir Visnovsky, who the Islanders were hoping could play the point on the power play, stayed in Slovakia with his K.H.L. team instead of reporting to camp.
abstract: New York Islanders defenseman Lubomir Visnovsky stays in Slovakia with his Kontinental Hockey League team instead of reporting to Islanders training camp.
lead_paragraph: Defenseman Lubomir Visnovsky, who the Islanders were hoping could play the point on the power play, stayed in Slovakia with his K.H.L. team instead of reporting to camp.

headline.seo: Islanders Unsure of Lubomir Visnovsky’s Return
headline.main: Islanders Unsure if They Will Get a Key Player Back
headline.print_headline: Islanders Unsure if They Will Get a Key Player Back
